{
  "vibe_title_en": "Sacred Alchemy",
  "master_prompt": "A hyper-realistic, surreal beauty portrait of The Protagonist, captured in a tight head-and-shoulders composition. The subject looks slightly upward with a hopeful, visionary expression, embodying the archetype of a modern oracle. THE SURREAL ELEMENT: Instead of a traditional necklace, a precise, geometric orbit of floating liquid mercury spheres and crystal-clear water droplets levitates around the subject's neck, defying gravity. These suspended spheres act as lenses, refracting the scene with physically accurate caustics. THE SETTING: A niche, tactile sanctuary built from translucent, rough-hewn alabaster blocks that glow with a warm, internal amber light. LIGHTING: A soft, divine top-light highlights the texture of the skin and the reflective surfaces of the floating liquid spheres, creating a cinematic 'halo' effect. TECH SPECS: Shot on Hasselblad H6D-100c, 100mm f/2.2 Macro lens. TEXTURE: Fine grain Kodak Portra 160 simulation to ground the surrealism in analog reality. No neon, no digital painting style—pure photographic surrealism.",
  "meta": {
    "intent": "Create a high-fashion surrealist portrait that blends ancient ritual aesthetics with impossible physics.",
    "priorities": "Photorealistic skin texture, accurate refraction in liquid elements, atmospheric depth.",
    "device_profile": "High-Resolution Studio Monitor"
  },
  "frame": {
    "aspect": "4:5",
    "composition": "Center-weighted tight portrait, focusing on the face and neck area.",
    "layout": "Symmetrical subject placement with negative space at the top.",
    "camera_angle": "Eye-level to slightly low angle to emphasize the 'Visionary' status.",
    "tilt_roll_degrees": "0 degrees"
  },
  "subject": {
    "gender": "Female",
    "identity": "The Protagonist (Universal Template)",
    "demographics": "Ageless, Ethereal",
